.SH NAME
.PP
kubectl create clusterrolebinding \- Create a ClusterRoleBinding for a particular ClusterRole


.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\fBkubectl create clusterrolebinding\fP [OPTIONS]


.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Create a ClusterRoleBinding for a particular ClusterRole.


